---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro'
const lastUpdated = '2026-06-10'
---

<Base
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Full disclaimer for Pilot.BM content. Not legal, immigration, tax, or financial advice."
>
  <section style="background-color: var(--color-sand); padding-block: var(--space-10);">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: var(--text-3xl);">Disclaimer</h1>
      <p style="color: var(--color-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm);">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container" style="padding-block: var(--space-12);">
    <div style="max-width: 720px;" class="prose">

      <div class="disclaimer-box" role="note" aria-label="Summary disclaimer">
        <p class="disclaimer-box__title">
          <span class="disclaimer-box__icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
          Summary: not professional advice of any kind
        </p>
        <p class="disclaimer-box__body">
          Nothing on this website is legal, immigration, tax, financial, or professional advice.
          Information is provided for general educational purposes only.
          Always verify current requirements at <a href="https://www.gov.bm" rel="noopener" target="_blank">gov.bm</a>
          and consult qualified professionals before making decisions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2>Informational purpose only</h2>
      <p>
        All content on Pilot.BM — including guides, tools, calculators, directory listings,
        and editorial articles — is provided for general informational and educational purposes only.
        It does not constitute and should not be relied upon as:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Legal advice</li>
        <li>Immigration advice</li>
        <li>Tax advice</li>
        <li>Financial advice</li>
        <li>Medical advice</li>
        <li>Professional advice of any kind</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>No guarantee of accuracy</h2>
      <p>
        Bermuda's regulations, fees, and policies change frequently. While we make reasonable efforts
        to keep information current, we cannot guarantee that every piece of information is accurate,
        complete, or up to date at the time you read it.
      </p>
      <p>
        The authoritative source for Bermuda government policies, fees, regulations, and procedures is
        the Government of Bermuda at <a href="https://www.gov.bm" rel="noopener" target="_blank">gov.bm</a>.
        For health insurance rates, the Bermuda Health Council at
        <a href="https://www.bhec.bm" rel="noopener" target="_blank">bhec.bm</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Work permits and immigration</h2>
      <p>
        Information about Bermuda work permits, immigration pathways, the EIRC, and related topics
        is provided for general educational purposes only. Immigration law is complex and individual
        circumstances vary significantly. Always consult a qualified Bermuda immigration attorney
        before making any immigration-related decisions.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Programme note:</strong> The Work From Bermuda digital-nomad programme closed permanently
        on 28 February 2025. Where this Site references that programme, it does so in the past tense
        or as a historical reference. Do not rely on any third-party source that presents it as current.
      </p>

      <h2>Compensation and financial calculators</h2>
      <p>
        Any calculators on this Site (including the Compensation Calculator) produce estimates only.
        Payroll tax rates, deductions, and other financial figures used in these calculators may be
        approximate or unverified. Results should be treated as a starting point for conversation
        with a qualified Bermuda accountant or employer, not as a definitive figure.
      </p>

      <h2>Directory listings</h2>
      <p>
        Business listings in the Pilot.BM directory are provided as a convenience. We do not endorse
        or guarantee the quality, accuracy, or safety of any listed business. Contact information,
        hours, and details may be outdated. Always verify directly with the business before relying
        on any listing information.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate links and sponsorship</h2>
      <p>
        Some links on this Site are affiliate links. We may earn a commission if you make a purchase
        through those links. Paid directory listings (Standard, Featured, Anchor tiers) are commercial
        arrangements. Our editorial coverage is not influenced by commercial relationships.
        See our full <a href="/legal/affiliate-disclosure">affiliate disclosure</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>External links</h2>
      <p>
        Links to third-party websites are provided for convenience. We are not responsible for the
        content, accuracy, or privacy practices of external sites.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you believe any information on this Site is materially inaccurate, please contact us at
        <a href="mailto:matt@ravenpower.net">matt@ravenpower.net</a>.
        We review all corrections and update promptly where warranted.
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
